            <div class="small-12 columns">
                <div class="social-media-links UA_ShareModalLinks" style="text-align: left;">
                    <a href="mailto:?&amp;subject=From%20MDPI%3A%20%22Unsupervised%20Anomaly%20Detection%20and%20Explanation%20in%20Network%20Traffic%20with%20Transformers&quot;&amp;body=https://www.mdpi.com/3050722%3A%0A%0AUnsupervised%20Anomaly%20Detection%20and%20Explanation%20in%20Network%20Traffic%20with%20Transformers

Deep%20learning-based%20autoencoders%20represent%20a%20promising%20technology%20for%20use%20in%20network-based%20attack%20detection%20systems.%20They%20offer%20significant%20benefits%20in%20managing%20unknown%20network%20traces%20or%20novel%20attack%20signatures.%20Specifically%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20critical%20infrastructures%2C%20such%20as%20power%20supply%20systems%2C%20AI-based%20intrusion%20detection%20systems%20must%20meet%20stringent%20requirements%20concerning%20model%20accuracy%20and%20trustworthiness.%20For%20the%20intrusion%20response%2C%20the%20activation%20of%20suitable%20countermeasures%20can%20greatly%20benefit%20from%20additional%20transparency%20information%20%28e.g.%2C%20attack%20causes%29.%20Transformers%20represent%20the%20state%20of%20the%20art%20for%20learning%20from%20sequential%20data%20and%20provide%20important%20model%20insights%20through%20the%20widespread%20use%20of%20attention%20mechanisms.%20This%20paper%20introduces%20a%20two-stage%20transformer-based%20autoencoder%20for%20learning%20meaningful%20information%20from%20network%20traffic%20at%20the%20packet%20and%20sequence%20level.%20Based%20on%20this%2C%20we%20present%20a%20sequential%20attention%20weight%20perturbation%20method%20to%20explain%20benign%20and%20malicious%20network%20packets.%20We%20evaluate%20our%20method%20against%20benchmark%20models%20and%20expert-based%20explanations%20using%20the%20CIC-IDS-2017%20benchmark%20dataset.%20The%20results%20show%20promising%20results%20in%20terms%20of%20detecting%20and%20explaining%20FTP%20and%20SSH%20brute-force%20attacks%2C%20highly%20outperforming%20the%20results%20of%20the%20benchmark%20model." title="Email">
                        <i class="fa fa-envelope-square" style="font-size: 30px;"></i>
                    </a>

                                        <a href="https://x.com/intent/tweet?text=Unsupervised+Anomaly+Detection+and+Explanation+in+Network+Traffic+with+Transformers&amp;hashtags=mdpielectronics&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F3050722&amp;via=electronicsMDPI" onclick="windowOpen(this.href,600,800); return false" title="Twitter" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
